title: [Guardian Keep, Inner Wall]
description: The imposing inner wall of the keep stretches off to the east and west, providing relief from the sun to many of the tents that line up near its base.  Merchants hawk their wares to the passing patrons and soldiers as they walk along well trampled pathways in the grassy courtyard.

The imposing inner wall of the keep stretches off to the east and west, the night's darkness disguises the shapes of the many tents that line up near its base.  Merchants hawk their wares to the passing patrons and soldiers as they walk along well trampled pathways in the grassy courtyard.
